<taxonomicName authorityName="Eger &amp; Lim" authorityYear="2011" box="[2056,2214,2264,2297]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="150" pageNumber="911" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="chrysochaetes">chrysochaetes</taxonomicName>
, and limited genetic data suggest they are closely related. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
